import SVGImg from './svg-1.svg';
export const homeObjOne = {
    id: 'about',
    lightBg: false,
    lightText: true,
    lightTextDesc: true,
    topLine: 'Premium Bank',
    headLine: 'Unlimited transaction with zero fees',
    description: 'get access to our exclusive app that allows you to send unlimited transaction without getting charge any fees.',
    buttonLabel: 'Get Started',
    imgStart: false,
    img: SVGImg,
    alt: 'Car',
    primary: true,
    darkText: false
};
